* Compute Permission Levels
** NO PERMISSIONS
***_ Cannot see or use compute
***_ Default state
** CAN ATTACH TO
***_ Attach notebooks
***_ View Spark UI
***_ View compute metrics
***_ Cannot start/stop/restart
** CAN RESTART
***_ Everything in CAN ATTACH TO
***_ Can terminate, start, restart
***_ Cannot change configuration
** CAN MANAGE
***_ Full control
***_ Edit configuration
***_ Attach libraries
***_ Resize cluster
***_ Modify others' permissions
***_ Workspace admins get this automatically
** Driver log access
***_ Default: CAN MANAGE only
***_ Logs may contain secrets
***_ Configurable via Spark property
@endmindmap
